%}

### 9ï¸âƒ£ Try to create duplicate plant
POST {{baseUrl}}/plants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rose",
  "scientificName": "Rosa duplicate",
  "habitat": "Test",
  "somethingInteresting": "This should fail"
}

> {%
    client.test("POST duplicate plant returns 409 Conflict", () => {
